Cross-validation for estimating tuning parameters.
dlda.cv <- function(dlda_obj, hold_out_size = 5, shrink = seq(0.01, 0.1, by = 0.01)) {
	Takes a dlda_obj
	Iterate through tuning params
	Determine optimal value
	Attach crossvalidation info to object, which can be passed to 
}

Example:
dlda_out <- dlda(train_df, diagonalize = TRUE)
	Has $B and $train_df attached to it.
dlda_out <- dlda_cv(dlda_out, hold_out_size = 5)
predict(dlda_out, test_df)

